<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie-edge">
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css">

    <title>Image uploads</title>
</head>
<body style="background-image: url('images/girl-embarcing-cat-and-dog.jpg');background-size: 100%">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s4 m4 l4" style="opacity: 80%">
                <div class="card" style="size: auto">
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <span class="card-title">Bienvenido/a!</span>
                        <p>Para contribuir con la base de datos, por favor seleccione un conjunto de imágenes pertenecientes a una misma mascota.</p>
                        <br>
                        <p>Muchas gracias!</p>
                        <br>
                        <div class="divider"></div>
                        <br>
                        <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                            <span>Tipo de mascota:</span>
                            <div class="row" style="margin-top: 10px">
                                <div class="col s6 m6 l6">
                                    <label>
                                        <input class="with-gap" name="selectedPet" type="radio" value="dog" checked />
                                        <span style="color: dimgrey">Perro</span>
                                    </label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col s6 m6 l6">
                                    <label>
                                        <input class="with-gap" name="selectedPet" type="radio" value="cat" />
                                        <span style="color: dimgrey">Gato</span>
                                    </label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="file-field input-field">
                                <div class="btn" style="background: lightseagreen">
                                    <span>Seleccionar</span>
                                    <input name="petImages" type="file" multiple>
                                </div>
                                <div class="file-path-wrapper">
                                    <label>
                                        <input class="file-path validate" type="text" placeholder="Subir entre 3 y 10 imágenes">
                                    </label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <blockquote style="border-color: green">
                                <%= typeof msg != 'undefined' ? msg : '' %>
                            </blockquote>
                            <br>
                            <div class="row">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn" style="background: salmon;float: right">Cargar imágenes</button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a href='https://www.freepik.es/fotos/perro' style="position:fixed; padding:5px; bottom:0px;">Foto de Perro creado por freepic.diller - www.freepik.es</a>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js" integrity="sha256-/xUj+3OJU5yExlq6GSYGSHk7tPXikynS7ogEvDej/m4=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/js/materialize.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
